                    <comment id="12683898" author="pjaol" created="Fri, 20 Mar 2009 14:45:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixes an NPE when using DistanceQueryBuilder for just minimal bounding box searches&lt;br/&gt;
e.g.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; DistanceQueryBuilder dq = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; DistanceQueryBuilder(
                                                         latitude, longitude,
                                                         radius,
                                                         latField, &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//name of latitude field in index
&lt;/span&gt;                                                         lngField, &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//name of longitude field in index
&lt;/span&gt;                                                         tierPrefix, &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// prefix of tier fields in index
&lt;/span&gt;                                                         &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;  /*filter by radius, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt; means mbb search */     );
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
